    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">Donnacha Oisín Kidney & Nicolas Wu · ICFP 2021 · <a href="https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/3473577">ACM</a></p>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Prereqs: <a href="/reading/natural-breadcrumbs/fritz-2020/">🍞 Fritz 2020</a> (Kleisli composition). Familiarity with monads helps.</p>

